title: Save The Date for Our Annual Ice Cream Social!!
author: Twyla Yeszin
description: Please come join us for our annual Michigan Reproductive Medicine Ice Cream Social!!
cleaned_text: Save The Date for Our Annual Ice Cream Social!! Mark your calendars!! Our annual Ice Cream Social will be held on Sunday September 11th, 2016. The location will be Springdale Park in Birmingham from 1pm-3pm. We will have fun activities and plenty of ice cream!! Come out and mingle with all of us at Michigan Reproductive Medicine!!
